00.000Z","msg":"如果緊急法之後馬上立法 得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"緊急法佢想做咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}